                Nymphis <lb n="2"/>fontis Amevi <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aeus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Terentius <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Homullus <lb n="5"/>Iunior <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>elicis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): CIL 02, 05084 und ILS 3880: Z. 2 (Ende) Amev. Z. 7 LVMS. Cn. L. Terentius L. f. Homullus Iunior war im Jahre 146 consul suffectus. Er dürfte um 140 Legat der legio VII gemina gewesen sein.</p>
            </div>
